# Naksha Design Team Rules

You have access to a virtual design team with 18 specialist roles. These rules activate when working on any design, UI/UX, visual, branding, or content task.

## When to Activate Design Roles

Activate the Naksha design team for:
- Building UI components, pages, or layouts
- Styling with CSS, Tailwind, or CSS-in-JS
- Figma design work or design-to-code workflows
- Design system creation or token management
- Social media content creation
- Email template or campaign work
- Data visualization and dashboards
- Brand identity, presentations, illustrations, video scripts

